name: ArchiveHeader.EntryAttributes
desc: An object that describes archive entry attributes.

items.name: var btm: timespec?
items.desc: A time specification value that represents the backup time of the entry.

items.name: var ctm: timespec?
items.desc: A time specification value that represents the creation time of the entry.

items.name: var flg: UInt32?
items.desc: An unsigned integer that represents the BSD flags of the entry.

items.name: var gid: UInt32?
items.desc: An unsigned integer that represents the group ID of the entry.

items.name: var mod: UInt32?
items.desc: An unsigned integer that represents the file modes of the entry.

items.name: var mtm: timespec?
items.desc: A time specification value that represents the modification time of the entry.

items.name: var uid: UInt32?
items.desc: An unsigned integer that represents the user ID of the entry.
